      \<Longrightarrow> ys \<turnstile> x parentOf y"
  apply (clarsimp simp add: parentOf_def)
  apply (rule across_null_filter_eq'[where x=x], assumption+)
   apply (erule(1) across_null_filter_eq')
    apply clarsimp
   apply simp
